title: Putin: The Mask is Off. Europe is Next. - Ep 162
itunes:title: Putin: The Mask is Off. Europe is Next. - Ep 162
description:
Vitaliy writes his most honest and grim take on the Ukraine war yet. Whereas before there was a veil of pretense about what Putin's war in Ukraine was about (NATO, "denazification"), that pretense is now gone.

Vitaliy shares why this is a war of conquest, and raises the alarm bell for the rest of Europe.

Four-part series on the war in Ukraine link: https://contrarianedge.com/tag/war-in-ukraine/

War in Ukraine: Part 4 – Are There Neo-Nazis in Ukraine? article link: https://contrarianedge.com/war-in-ukraine-part-4-are-there-neo-nazis-in-ukraine/

You can read this article online here: https://contrarianedge.com/putin-the-mask-is-off-europe-is-next/
